							<p class="seprator">|</p>
<div class="slug"><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=15489&query=Interview" class="js-clickTrack" data-category="Article" data-action="Breadcrumbs Section" data-label="Interview">Interview</a></div>
</span></div><div class="meta-container " itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><h1 class="title article-title" itemprop="name">Pop Goes the Worship</h1><div class="deck spacer-top-20 spacer-bottom-15" itemprop="description">Religion professor T. David Gordon says Muzak has shaped singing in church.</div>
<div class="article-byline "><span class="author" itemprop="author">Interview by Mark Moring</span><span class="pipe">|</span><span class="postdate" itemprop="datePublished"><time datetime="2011-3-9">March 9, 2011 </time></span></div>
<div class="article-languages spacer-top-5"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section><section class="article-featured-image "><div class="container"><figure class="p-relative align-center spacer-top-40"><img class="img-responsive" src="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/64871.jpg?h=528&w=940" width="940" alt="Pop Goes the Worship" title="Pop Goes the Worship" /></figure><figcaption class="spacer-top-5 spacer-bottom-5"><div class="credit ">
									Image:
									
										Richard Kelly Photography
									</div>
</figcaption></div></section><section class="container"><div class="spacer-top-25 u-cf social-nav-item"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/system/social/css/share.css?09262023"></link>
				<div
					class="ctSocialShare ctSocialShare_horizontal ctSocialShare_fallback"
					style="display: none; visibility: hidden; opacity: 0"
